			<p>I use cpanel and had a lil bit of a prob using this as is.. This is what I ended up doing..</p>
<p>1. I didn&#8217;t create a subdomain I just created a cname for mobile and made that point to my domainname.com</p>
<p>2. $SERVER["SERVER_NAME"] didn&#8217;t have &#8220;mobile.mydomain.com&#8221; so I ended up using $SERVER["HTTP_HOST"] instead</p>
<p>everything worked as is..</p>

