			<p>A tiny improvement to the image regexp &#8211; you can ditch the unused backreferences, so:</p>
<p>$buffer = preg_replace(’/(<a>]*&gt;)(?:]+alt=”)([^"]*)(?:”[^&gt;]*&gt;)()/i’, ‘$1$2$3’, $buffer);</a></p>

